    <li>Must only be used on the <a href="//www.st-andrews.ac.uk/about/governance/">governance pages</a>.</li>
	<li>The biography excerpt should be no more than 140 characters.</li>
	<li>The profile image must be 200 &times; 200 pixels.</li>
	<li>An image must be present if using a link to a full biography.</li>
	<li>The heading link and the full biography link must be the same.</li>
	<li>Contact information should be present if available.</li>
</ul>

